reviewText: Did not like would not work
It didn't work had to get refund and send back very disappointed
if you love Mickey and the gang, you need this dvd too.

Apparently the video I recieved was from a country other than the U.S. because it wouldn't play in my DVD player. Said it was a region error. So I've now learned to check where the DVD i order is coming from. I'm out $$ and have a DVD she can't watch.
I didn't know it is for Region 2 -- Europe.  Amazon should show an obvious warning if customer is from the U.S.!
